                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d475">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Ambassador <persName type="from">Dudley</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Extract.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Petropolis</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-05-18">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 18, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Reference department’s May 15. Rio Branco to-day assented to proposed publication
                    of joint note in the three capitals. Publication here, though complete as a
                    Portuguese translation, may purport to be a résumé.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dudley.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
